videos.description: North Carolina running back Michael Carter goes straight through the middle of the defense to put UNC on the board early.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carter strolls through middle of Western Carolina's D for TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter strolls through middle of Western Carolina's D for TD

videos.description: Sam Howell fires the pass to Antoine Green, who goes 22 yards for the North Carolina score.

videos.headline: Howell hits Green with quick pass for UNC TD

videos.description: Michael Carter runs 22 yards right up the middle of Western Carolina's defense for his second touchdown of the game for North Carolina.

videos.headline: UNC's Carter darts through the defense for his second TD

videos.description: Sam Howell hits a wide-open Dazz Newsome for a 26-yard touchdown to increase North Carolina's lead.
